works.description: My article titled "What Do Crocodiles Eat | Crocodiles Diet" published by me at animalstime.com on 7 July, 2012 is infringed by the text excerpted on the site mammalz.com, beginning with the text "How many of you know what do crocodiles eat? A crocodile is a wild animal that belongs to the family of Crocodylidae. These reptiles are sometimes referred to as aquatic species which is due to the fact that crocodiles spend most of their time under water."
